text: The Last Image (, translit. Al-coura al-akhira, ) is a 1986 Algerian drama movie directed by Mohammed Lakhdar-Hamina and stars Véronique Jannot, Merwan Lakhdar-Hamina, Michel Boujenah, Jean Bouise, Jean-François Balmer. It was distributed by Cannon Films. ==Other websites== * Category:1986 drama movies Category:Algerian movies Category:Movies directed by Mohammed Lakhdar-Hamina
